longBusinessSummary: Environmental Packaging Technologies Holdings, Inc., through its subsidiary, Environmental Packaging Technologies, Inc., provides packaging solutions for the transport and storage of bulk products primarily in the United States, Korea, and the Netherlands. The company manufactures flexitank, a soft sided single use container enabling bulk shipment of non-hazardous liquids, including latex and other chemicals, edible oils, wine, petroleum based products, and others. It also provides packaging supply/installation, loading and unloading, product transfer, product stewardship, removal-disposal-recycling, and logistic services. The company offers its products under the BIG Red Flexitank, BIG Red Wine-Pac, and BIG Red LIQUIRIDE names to shipping companies, logistics companies, manufacturer suppliers, and consumer product manufacturers in approximately 50 countries worldwide. The company was formerly known as International Metals Streaming Corp. The company was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Houston, Texas.
